text: #Ontario has surpassed one million mark in #vaccine doses administered. As of 8 pm Wed, 1,019,407 shots given. 281,714 people in the province fully vaccinated. Health #Canada says 1.5% of the country's population has been fully vaccinated so far. (Image: CP/Frank Gunn) #COVID19 https://t.co/ivfwG6Fpvr
